                    <span>In every chapter I learned something helpful to improve my communications, not only at work but also at home.  I especially like the author's concept of "building bridges" and the specific skills for doing so.  <p>It has helped me a great deal with my co-workers and personnel.  I plan on suggesting this book as a "must do" for my staff!!</span>
                  
              
